trans-unit.source: The <see cref="N:System.Collections.Specialized" /> namespace contains specialized and strongly-typed collections; for example, a linked list dictionary, a bit vector, and collections that contain only strings.
trans-unit.target: O namespace <see cref="N:System.Collections.Specialized" /> contém coleções especializadas e fortemente tipadas; por exemplo, um dicionário de lista vinculada, um vetor de bits e coleções que contêm somente cadeias de caracteres.

trans-unit.source: Specialized collections are collections with highly specific purposes.
trans-unit.target: Coleções especializadas são coleções com finalidades altamente específicas.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection> is based on <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase>; however, <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection> accepts multiple values per key, whereas <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase> accepts only one value per key.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection> é baseado no <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase>; no entanto, <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection> aceita vários valores por chave, enquanto <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase> aceita apenas um valor por chave.

trans-unit.source: Some strongly typed collections in the <xref:System.Collections.Specialized> namespace are <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection> and <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringDictionary>, both of which contain values that are exclusively strings.
trans-unit.target: Algumas coleções fortemente tipadas no <xref:System.Collections.Specialized> namespace são <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringCollection> e <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.StringDictionary>, que contêm valores que são exclusivamente cadeias de caracteres.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.CollectionsUtil> class creates instances of case-insensitive collections.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.CollectionsUtil> classe cria instâncias de coleções de maiusculas e minúsculas.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.HybridDictionary> class starts as a <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.ListDictionary> and becomes a <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> when it becomes large.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.HybridDictionary> classe inicia como um <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.ListDictionary> e se torna um <xref:System.Collections.Hashtable> quando ele se torna grande.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.KeyedCollection%602> is a list but it also creates a lookup dictionary when the number of elements reaches a specified threshold.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.KeyedCollection%602> é uma lista, mas ele também cria um dicionário de pesquisa quando o número de elementos atinge um limite especificado.
